1) Pascal Triangle
  i) Find nth row's and cth column value
  ii) Find the row values 
  iii) Print entire triangle

1) Pascal Triangle
  i) Find nth row's and cth column value
  def ncr(n,r):
    res=1
    for i in range(r):
        res = res*(n-i)
        res=res//(i+1)
    return res
  n = int(input())
  r = int(input())
  print(ncr(n,r)

  ii) Find the row values 
  def ncr(n,r):
    res=1
    for i in range(r):
        res = res*(n-i)
        res=res//(i+1)
    return res
  def value(n):
      for i in range(n):
          print(ncr(n-1,i),end=" ")
      print()
  n = int(input())
  r = int(input())
  value(n)

  iii) Print entire triangle
